    "text": {
      "en": "We are Yummi Go, a platform providing catering services for events and projects of all sizes. We offer fresh, daily meals for employees of companies and factories, with high quality and reliable service. Our goal is to provide a comfortable and dependable experience that gives you peace of mind… and elevates every detail of your hospitality and catering needs.",
